50|$|After the Slovak {{parliamentary}} election, 1994, {{members of}} the parliament representing HZDS arranged {{for a change in}} the law, making the parliament elect the head of the <b>Slovak</b> <b>Secret</b> <b>Service,</b> instead of the President. On April 18, 1995 Vladimír Mečiar named Ivan Lexa the Director of <b>Slovak</b> <b>Secret</b> <b>Service.</b>|$|E
