50|$|Code of the <b>Secret</b> <b>Service</b> is a 1939 film {{directed}} by Noel M. Smith and starring Ronald Reagan. It {{is the second}} of four films in the U.S. <b>Secret</b> <b>Service</b> Agent Brass Bancroft series, having been preceded by <b>Secret</b> <b>Service</b> of the Air (1939) and followed by Smashing the Money Ring (1939) and Murder in the Air (1940).|$|R
